    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899060/extras/a6a952c2f93a77709f42685a79a4f810.avif?t=1760438577\" width=600 height=200 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >欢迎来到一个奇幻又黑暗的世界，现实和梦境交织在一起，每个角落都潜伏着秘密……</h2><br><br>《化妆镜》是一款超现实的独立冒险游戏，将带你踏上一段穿越神秘国度的旅程。在那里，凡事都没有表面这么单纯，所有事物都息息相关。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899060/extras/53f6f6004abd716186518138545e5ff8.poster.avif?t=1760438577\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899060/extras/53f6f6004abd716186518138545e5ff8.webm?t=1760438577\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899060/extras/53f6f6004abd716186518138545e5ff8.mp4?t=1760438577\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>你扮演一个过去扑朔迷离的小女孩，在一间陌生又诡异的屋子里醒来，身边只有你手上的化妆镜。为了寻回记忆，你必须探索这栋建筑的扭曲走廊及房间、解决谜题、与独特的角色互动，并揭开关于你的身份以及邪恶力量的真相。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899060/extras/c21486235af4f16e3a438763a117adb8.poster.avif?t=1760438577\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899060/extras/c21486235af4f16e3a438763a117adb8.webm?t=1760438577\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899060/extras/c21486235af4f16e3a438763a117adb8.mp4?t=1760438577\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>你有办法面对真相吗？</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899060/extras/6323859fc56357c87f9b288b87e40496.poster.avif?t=1760438577\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899060/extras/6323859fc56357c87f9b288b87e40496.webm?t=1760438577\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899060/extras/6323859fc56357c87f9b288b87e40496.mp4?t=1760438577\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>《化妆镜》具有美得令人难忘的美术风格、扣人心弦的配乐和引人入胜的故事情节，带来独一无二又难以忘怀的游戏体验。它会挑战你的思维、触动你的心灵，令你惊叹不已。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899060/extras/eb67db360804814e53a654b997850f0f.poster.avif?t=1760438577\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899060/extras/eb67db360804814e53a654b997850f0f.webm?t=1760438577\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899060/extras/eb67db360804814e53a654b997850f0f.mp4?t=1760438577\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>超现实且氛围独特的世界，满满的谜团和奇观等你一探究竟<br></li><li>有趣的谜题和挑战，考验你的技巧和逻辑<br></li><li>令人印象深刻又复杂的角色<br></li><li>多种路线与结局，取决于你的选择和行动<br></li><li>余音绕梁的优美配乐，令人沉浸于游戏氛围<br></li><li>丰富且深刻的世界观，满足探索欲和好奇心<br></li><li>一段刻骨铭心的自我发现、失落和希望之旅</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899060/extras/04dfdaf315d9d58f663b38c3258434f7.poster.avif?t=1760438577\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899060/extras/04dfdaf315d9d58f663b38c3258434f7.webm?t=1760438577\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899060/extras/04dfdaf315d9d58f663b38c3258434f7.mp4?t=1760438577\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >绝对不要放开它，明白吗？</h2>",
